@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### 健康檢查
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 列出圖片
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/images?limit=10

### 上傳並辨識（multipart）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/images/upload-and-classify
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

我的貓
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cat.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_images/cat.jpg
------Boundary--

### 取得單張圖片
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/images/1

### 純 AI 分類（不入庫）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/classify
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cat.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_images/cat.jpg
------Boundary--

### 上傳並入庫（不辨識）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/images/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

測試圖片
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cat.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_images/cat.jpg
------Boundary--

### Ollama 描述圖片
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/describe
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="prompt"

請以繁體中文描述這張圖片
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cat.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_images/cat.jpg
------Boundary--

### OCR 文字辨識
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/ocr
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="text.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test_images/text.png
------Boundary--

### 影像生成（OpenAI DALL·E）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/generate
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

prompt=A cute corgi wearing sunglasses on a beach, watercolor style

### 啟動非同步生成
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/generate-async
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

prompt=A futuristic city at night, cyberpunk style

### 查詢任務狀態（換成上一行回傳的 task_id）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/tasks/REPLACE_TASK_ID

### Redis 快取統計
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/cache/stats

### 透過依賴注入測試 Redis
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/cache-test

### 純 JSON 建立（教材 3.2 範例）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/demo/images
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "我的貓",
  "url": "https://example.com/cat.jpg",
  "tags": ["cat", "pet"]
}

### 練習 1：JSONPlaceholder 取單張
GET https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/photos/1

### 練習 2：相簿圖片列表
GET https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/photos?albumId=1

### 練習 3：建立新圖片紀錄
POST https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/photos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "albumId": 1,
  "title": "我的圖片",
  "url": "https://example.com/img.jpg"
}

### 練習 4：完整更新
PUT https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/photos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "albumId": 1,
  "id": 1,
  "title": "更新標題",
  "url": "https://example.com/new.jpg"
}

### 練習 5：刪除
DELETE https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/photos/1
